name: Elliya_Fabric_White_Nailheads_Parsons_Chairs_(Set_of_2)
reviews: These chairs are sturdy and comfortable. Bought 8 of them for my new dining room and totally love them.
description:
The Elliya Fabric Nailheads Parsons Chair makes for a gorgeous addition to any table setup. Its neat and simple structural design is complemented by the classy choice of colors used, which makes this set of chairs highly compatible with most decor styles. The frames are made from top drawer wood, which makes these chairs highly durable and extremely stable.

The chairs are crafted with a wooden frame and upholstered in a seafoam blue or sandy tan fabric, with cherry finish legs and decorative nailheads.
